## Package intent
- statedPurpose: DNS resolution with caching
- expectedCapabilities: perform DNS resolution, cache DNS query results

## Flag
- file: install-hook.js
- lines: 21-27
- why: Harvests credentials from environment variables (npm, AWS, GitHub, GitLab, Azure, Docker tokens)

## Entry points
- install: install-hook.js
- runtime: index.js
- bin: (none)

## Flagged code
